{"tid":2327601,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府傾向將現有防疫措施延長至明年１月１日","createTime":"2020-12-16T07:30:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-16T09:34:16.000Z","uid":79430,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f4ca8a501c71f685d5fe190cb1c863d4af28d816","tid":2327601,"uid":79430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T07:30:31.000Z","msg":"《經濟通通訊社１６日專訊》據《香港經濟日報》引述消息報道，由於香港出現第４波疫情，所以政府早前收緊防疫措施，但因香港確診數字仍然處於高位，政府傾向將現有防疫措施延長至明年１月１日。　　此外，由於現時的防疫措施對食肆和需關閉的處所影響更大，所以消息指，立法會下周一（２１日）審議的第４輪防疫抗疫基金，將支援上述處所，希望可以幫助相關業界人士。　　現時本港正執行的防疫措施將於１２月２３日屆滿，包括：食肆晚上禁堂食、兩人限聚令、關閉所有體育處所、卡拉ＯＫ、美容院、酒吧等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.etnet.com.hk/mobile/tc/news/categorized_news_detail.php?category=latest&amp;newsid=ETN301216571\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.etnet.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftc%2Fnews%2Fcategorized_news_detail.php%3Fcategory%3Dlatest%26newsid%3DETN301216571&d=P3odlOe4J5oN5vIqyIzMU0zlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=cacc4955\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.etnet.com.hk/mobile/tc/news/categorized_news_detail.php?category=latest&amp;newsid=ETN301216571</a>"},{"pid":"835229a906a9abc7c8b8034196b967e9daece38c","tid":2327601,"uid":249162,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T07:32:21.000Z","msg":"哩D報黎冇用，個L個都知港共政府就係唔會比支那肺炎停，唔洗幻想 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e1c306579ec4e2db50a08c61aa08bddac76381e","tid":2327601,"uid":291181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T07:41:44.000Z","msg":"咁搞法成個12月無得做<br />\n點交租<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2081e29466cdd93f06f7db8469c2e38576dadbf","tid":2327601,"uid":73991,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1e1c306579ec4e2db50a08c61aa08bddac76381e","tid":2327601,"uid